name: NameBox
0:
”Alexa, ask Name Box to give me a Chinese Female name.”
”Spell it.”
”Another one.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: name box
des: This skill gives you a random name for each request based on the conditions you set. The conditions include gender and category. The categories are mostly countries and regions, but there are also things like pet, hippy, history etc. The data was from https://www.behindthename.com/api.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
